  <brief_title>A Change in Diet May Decrease the Negative Consequences of Chronic Sleep Deprivation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study: A Dietary Intervention May Decrease the Negative Metabolic and Cognitive Consequences of Chronic Sleep Deprivation</official_title>
